System:

    melt of 100 chains of 8 atoms.

Usage:

Parallel NVE md simulation on 4 processors:

    mpirun -np 4 ddSim -e -p param.nve -c commands

Parallel NVT md simulation on 4 processors:

    mpirun -np 4 ddSim -e -p param.nvt -c commands

Restarting and extending:

    mpirun -np 4 ddSim -e -r restart -c commands.rst
